Waktu sedang santai dan ngopi, ada kucing liar lagi tidur di atas panel listrik. Tidurnya nyenyak banget, difoto lucu kali ya. 

Eh tiba-tiba dia kebangun, tapi tetap anteng pas gw foto-foto. Coba liat aja sendiri.

-------

While relaxing and drinking coffee, there was a stray cat sleeping on an electrical panel. It slept calmly, then I thought it would made cute photographs.

Suddenly he woke up, but still posed for me. See for yourself.
